Package net.swofty.hyperlandsapi

Class Connection

java.lang.Object
net.swofty.hyperlandsapi.Connection
public class Connection extends Object
The class that handles all of the outgoing connections to the API Note that even though all calls are async, they are dependent on the Connection object So if you call two different API method with the same Connection object they will wait for one another
